#

Blackened Salmon with Mango Salsa

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishCitrus

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodDinnerHealthy

Description

A flavorful and vibrant dish that combines spicy blackened salmon with fresh mango salsa, perfect for a healthy dinner.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Cajun seasoning: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Mango: 1, diced
  • Red bell pepper: 1/2, diced
  • Red onion: 1/4, diced
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
